Dennis Naku, Port Harcourt A former leader of Rivers State House of Assembly, Dr. Chidi Lloyd, has dumped the All Progressives Congress for the Peoples Democratic Party. Lloyd, an ally to the Minister of Transportation, Rotimi Amaechi, was formally received at the Government House, Port Harcourt by Governor Nyesom Wike, and some PDP leaders on Monday. The former House leader apologised for the crisis that took place at the State House of Assembly in 2013. Details laterâ€¦